room_title: Escape room "Pinetti's Prestige" by Big Sky Breakout in Missoula
room_description: A well known Montana magician, Giovanni Piero Pinetti, disappears during an impressive trick over 100 years ago, never heard from again. Some said it was his last best trick others suspected foul play. We have uncovered a secret workshop here in the big yellow house and we invite you to solve the mystery of the brilliant Illusionist. Will you be able to uncover what really happened before you too disappear?
